This paper discusses privacy challenges in the context of the Internet of Things (IoT) and the collection and processing of large amounts of data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), which deals with privacy and security issues in computer systems. The paper also discusses data processing and aggregation, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.DB (Databases). Additionally, the paper addresses privacy concerns, which could be relevant to cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
